{"type": "article", "id": 59889, "title": "苹果评出 Ins 年度 Top 9 照片，抖音买了时报广场跨年最醒目广告位 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-02T05:30:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5036, "name": "跨年"}, {"id": 13247, "name": "李维斯"}, {"id": 48802, "name": "抖音"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190102120114knFlecO6W1dtIh3p.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"v663\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4323608610015901?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>蔡徐坤成为李维斯 2019 年度品牌代言人，</b></a>上一年度是陈伟霆。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j0821enude1\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4323755080062427?\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">佟丽娅成为馥蕾诗 2019 品牌代言人，</a>同时馥蕾诗将在全球发售新产品眼部精华。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l08217kkboy\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><br></p><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"jPiS\"><a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/51151691.html?weibo_id=4323666991493312\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>可口可乐和菜鸟裹裹推出心意定制瓶，</b></a>用支付宝 AR 扫一扫玩游戏，来为快递小哥送祝福。限量版已经在郑州、青岛、济南上市。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121213o3aRHcpe9ysjTdLI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.150926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"ON4s\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4323953982289588?\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>科颜氏为明星产品高保湿面霜在冰岛拍了支广告片，</b></a>由代言人刘昊然出镜演绎。意在表达升级后的新版本更加保湿，选择以遥远的严寒之地为背景，展现品牌不断挑战自己。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a08226rxhn6\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"ON4s\"><b><a href=\"https://designtaxi.com/news/403000/Nike-Unveils-2019-Chinese-New-Year-Collection-Inspired-By-All-12-Zodiac-Signs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 发布 2019 年农历新年别注球鞋系列，</a></b>设计上采用了中国传统育儿习俗“百家衣”理念。现在还没确切发售时间，预计是本月上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121236JHShztMG1FmbPl02.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121240hnLz3T0fQBXA9dYW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121236qH1CwfbmgT8eAFpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.986667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121237trhqKx4RzDw9A65m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121240KxJi9NUscelnwB8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"VBMB\"><b><a href=\"https://m.cnbeta.com/wap/view/803999.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">抖音租下纽约时报广场跨年最醒目的广告位。</a></b>时报广场水晶球落下的位置，背后的广告牌是抖音，在过去的 10 年里，这个位置一直是东芝的。东芝于 2017 年 11 月，宣布终止广告位合约。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121259jhKb9yJZO5aASloL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.581429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"0qUA\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BsBTzZRl08o/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苹果 Instagram 账户评出了 2018 年 9 张最受喜爱的照片，</b></a>这些照片都是由 iPhone 拍摄的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121551KuASBi9eRHOwN0GJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121551RV2fCs8e1ZThWX03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121552iuAPWVOXmEhUTJGr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901021215502af6YtHnuQOCLvx3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.246296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121553rxMgI8GX7ERSJsTl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121553qum9xZcSIzT8Yipb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121555WBup25TZVJ4ro3eY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121556QWzNXt5k9gcRrnJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190102121556KkhTC43HwQ1xqLIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.otsuka.co.jp/orc/campaign/genkihatsuratsunoyu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oronamin C在 JR 涩谷站推出了主题足浴店</a>，</b>除了足浴之外，还可以参与现场的互动活动。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901021501371kFQCX5vK4GOli0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@josephyates_\" rel=\"nofollow\">@josephyates_</a>&nbsp;on Unsplash<br></p>"}